sequenceDiagram
   participant Student
   participant FocusTimeSystem
   participant TimerService


   Student->>FocusTimeSystem: Pause Focus Session
   activate FocusTimeSystem
   FocusTimeSystem->>TimerService: Pause Timer
   activate TimerService
   TimerService-->>FocusTimeSystem: Timer Paused
   deactivate TimerService
   FocusTimeSystem-->>Student: Confirm Pause
   deactivate FocusTimeSystem


   Student->>FocusTimeSystem: Resume Focus Session
   activate FocusTimeSystem
   FocusTimeSystem->>TimerService: Resume Timer
   activate TimerService
   TimerService-->>FocusTimeSystem: Timer Running
   deactivate TimerService
   FocusTimeSystem-->>Student: Session Resumed
   deactivate FocusTimeSystem
